### Welcome to Groovy-eclipse.
This page hosts the eclipse update site for Will's fixes to the groovy-eclipse plugin.

Use http://will-lauer.github.io/groovy-eclipse/site-45 as the Mars update site and http://will-lauer.github.io/groovy-eclipse/site-46 as the Neon Update site.
